<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الضُّحَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{وَالضُّحَى , وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا سَجَى , مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَى}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٢:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c3">{إِذَا سَجَى}</span>: اسْتَوَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{سَجَى}</span>: أَظْلَمَ وَسَكَنَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الضحى: ١ - ٣]</p> </div>